{"tid":893614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"食麵加港幣七蚊多「一隻雞」 台食客加完驚覺「中伏」","createTime":"2018-11-07T19:03:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T05:38:38.000Z","uid":22675,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ef4b29e63aa09fa0bea82d262ef981a9afbdb738","tid":893614,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T19:03:14.000Z","msg":"2018-11-06 07:18中國<br />\n <img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181106/_2018110607214659886.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181106%2F_2018110607214659886.jpg&h=5e63f5a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n加七蚊多的「一隻雞」。網上圖片<br />\n台灣一名食客近日在一間某餐廳點了一碗雞絲麵後，老闆突然表示加30元新台幣(約7.8港元）就能多一隻雞，他當時聽到如此便宜立即加點，結果雞絲麵上枱時他才發現「中伏」。<br />\n<br />\n食客在Facebook專頁「爆廢公社」上載圖片，見到麵上確實多了「一隻雞」，但並不是真正的雞肉，而是一片黃色小雞造型的魚板。令他最不滿的不是魚板不好吃，而是小小的魚板竟要多收30元新台幣，認為老闆存心詐騙。"},{"pid":"e552b50bd92542b8a61887a05b4eb4d65c8d7f40","tid":893614,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T19:04:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/857455-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E9%A3%9F%E9%BA%B5%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%83%E8%9A%8A%E5%A4%9A%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%80%E9%9A%BB%E9%9B%9E%E3%80%8D+%E5%8F%B0%E9%A3%9F%E5%AE%A2%E5%8A%A0%E5%AE%8C%E9%A9%9A%E8%A6%BA%E3%80%8C%E4%B8%AD%E4%BC%8F%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F857455-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B-%25E9%25A3%259F%25E9%25BA%25B5%25E5%258A%25A0%25E4%25B8%2583%25E8%259A%258A%25E5%25A4%259A%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%259A%25BB%25E9%259B%259E%25E3%2580%258D%2B%25E5%258F%25B0%25E9%25A3%259F%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25AE%258C%25E9%25A9%259A%25E8%25A6%25BA%25E3%2580%258C%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E4%25BC%258F%25E3%2580%258D&d=AxaesQMkYMRry7IeotVFUf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0d142fea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstan